OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDrier for a
OL,6,Ftime this evening. Strengthening winds
OL,7,Fwill then herald a band of heavier
OL,8,Frain later in the night. Gusty winds
OL,9,Fparticularly near Bristol Channel
OL,10,Fcoasts. Temperatures holding up and
OL,11,Fstaying frost free.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRain soon clearing to the
OL,14,Feast tomorrow with sunny spells and
OL,15,Fblustery scattered showers following.
OL,16,FThese locally heavy with hail and a
OL,17,Frisk of thunder by the afternoon.
OL,18,FWindier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
