OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FUnsettled on Sunday and Monday with a
OL,7,Fmixture of sunny spells and showers.
OL,8,FRain possible on Tuesday. Temperatures
OL,9,Fgenerally close to average. Breezy at
OL,10,Ftimes, especially around showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
